'''Alexander Adams''' is the moniker that '''Grover Gardner''' uses when narrating various audiobooks include for the ''[[Star Wars]]'' audiobooks that he narrated. Adams also narrates under the moniker '''Tom Parker'''.<ref name="Audiofile interview" /> Adams first contribution to ''Star Wars'' franchise was narrating the [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace (unabridged audiobook)|unabridged audiobook]] for the [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace (novelization)|''Star Wars: The Phantom Menace'' novelization]]<ref name="Episode I">[[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace (unabridged audiobook)|''Star Wars: The Phantom Menace'' unabridged audiobook]]</ref> Adams would go on to narrate several abridged ''Star Wars'' audiobooks including five for the ''[[Star Wars: The New Jedi Order]]'' novel series.<ref name="The New Jedi Order">''[[Star Wars: The New Jedi Order]]''</ref>

